[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":651},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fhexo\u002F20201010\u002F1989721020\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fhexo\u002F20201010\u002F1989721020\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fhexo\u002F20201010\u002F1989721020\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fhexo\u002F20201010\u002F1989721020\u002F":628,"related:\u002Fhexo\u002F20201010\u002F1989721020\u002F":637},"\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2020\u002F10\u002F10\u002Flearn-hexo-27-github-actions-deploy\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":612,"date":613,"description":18,"extension":614,"lang":615,"meta":616,"navigation":178,"path":617,"readingMinutes":618,"seo":619,"standalone":620,"stem":621,"tags":622,"tldr":625,"updated":625,"url":626,"__hash__":627},"content\u002F試著學 Hexo\u002F27-試著學-Hexo-奇淫技巧-自動化部屬-GitHub-Actions.md","(27) 試著學 Hexo - 奇淫技巧 - 自動化部屬(GitHub Actions)","1989721020",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":603},"minimark",[11,15,19,23,30,33,41,51,57,60,64,67,84,87,90,94,97,103,107,110,113,119,123,133,138,141,152,462,465,471,474,481,539,542,588,591,599],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"接下來將會介紹另一款 CI，也就是 GitHub Actions。",[12,20,22],{"id":21},"github-actions","GitHub Actions",[16,24,25],{},[26,27],"img",{"alt":28,"src":29},"我希望私密儲存庫也可以自動部署","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-09-16%2015.50.43.png",[16,31,32],{},"我相信也有一些人會希望私密儲存庫也可以自動部署，畢竟有些文章可能不是那麼早公開，因為可能還在撰寫中等等，但又不想拋棄自動部屬，雖然我自己是沒有在使用自動部屬，因為我修改文章頻率很高，每次都會先做一點然後就 commit 上去做版本控制，依照我這種操作行為應該很快就炸了 XD?",[16,34,35,36,40],{},"回歸正題，上一篇雖然介紹了許多開源專案在使用的 Travis CI，但礙於它只接受開源專案免費使用，私密專案你就必須使用企業版，對於一個小部落客來講實在太傷荷包，因此好在 ",[37,38,39],"del",{},"微軟爸爸收購了 GitHub","（哎？）是 GitHub 本身有提供一個 CI 服務叫做 GitHub Actions，這個服務剛剛好可以符合我們需求，因此這邊只需要注意幾件事情，GitHub Actions 本身是有限制的",[42,43,44,48],"ul",{},[45,46,47],"li",{},"每個帳號只有運作 2,000 min (執行時間)，折合下來約 33.3333 小時",[45,49,50],{},"升級 Pro 之後也不是無限使用，頂多再多 1500 min",[16,52,53,54,56],{},"但 GitHub Actions 就如我所說，好在 ",[37,55,39],{},"（哎？）GitHub 佛心，約每 15 天就會重置一次，因此對於一個小部落客以及執行時間只要幾秒的專案來講，其實很足夠了。",[16,58,59],{},"因此接下來就會直接跳入主題，建立私密儲存庫的部分就不會教學了，畢竟跟公開儲存庫建立方式一樣，只是變成私密而已",[12,61,63],{"id":62},"生成-ssh-部署專用-key","生成 ssh 部署專用 key",[16,65,66],{},"首先我們要使用 GitHub Actions 之前你必須先生成 ssh Key，你只需要在你的電腦終端機輸入以下指令就可以生成一組私鑰(actions-deploy-key)和公鑰(actions-deploy-key.pub)",[68,69,74],"pre",{"className":70,"code":71,"language":72,"meta":73,"style":73},"language-cmd shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","ssh-keygen -f actions-deploy-key\n","cmd","",[75,76,77],"code",{"__ignoreMap":73},[78,79,82],"span",{"class":80,"line":81},"line",1,[78,83,71],{},[16,85,86],{},"(如果出現要你輸入密碼「Enter passphrase (empty for no passphrase): 」請不要輸入，直接按下 Enter 就好。)",[16,88,89],{},"基本上這段指令會基於你目前終端機位置來生成檔案。",[12,91,93],{"id":92},"新增私鑰到-github-私密儲存庫","新增私鑰到 GitHub 私密儲存庫",[16,95,96],{},"接下來將 「actions-deploy-key」私藥新增到私密儲存庫的 Settings -> Secrets -> Add a new secret 即可",[16,98,99],{},[26,100],{"alt":101,"src":102},"Add a new secret","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F1600243787720.jpg",[12,104,106],{"id":105},"新增公鑰到-blog-儲存庫","新增公鑰到 Blog 儲存庫",[16,108,109],{},"新增完私密之後，接下來要將「actions-deploy-key.pub」新增到部落格的儲存庫「xxxx.github.io」將公鑰增加到公開儲存庫的 Setting -> Deploy Keys -> Add deploy key 即可。",[16,111,112],{},"記得這邊要勾選一下「Allow write access Can this key be used to push to this repository? Deploy keys always have pull access.」否則會無法推進去。",[16,114,115],{},[26,116],{"alt":117,"src":118},"Add deploy key","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F1600244128684.jpg",[12,120,122],{"id":121},"建立-acions","建立 Acions",[16,124,125,126,129,130],{},"首先要在 Hexo 專案資料夾建立一個 .github 資料夾並且在新增一個資料夾叫做 ",[75,127,128],{},"workflows","，因此這邊會有兩層資料夾，最後在建立一個檔案叫做 ",[75,131,132],{},"hexoAcions.yml",[16,134,135],{},[26,136],{"alt":132,"src":137},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-09-16%2017.37.59.png",[16,139,140],{},"至於內容的部分我直接貼上",[16,142,143,144,147,148,151],{},"再次請務必注意 ",[75,145,146],{},"git config --global user.name \"xxxx\""," 與 ",[75,149,150],{},"git config --global user.email \"xxxx@gmail.com\""," 記得修改成自己 GitHub 名稱與 Email，若沒有填寫正確是無法正常運作的唷~",[68,153,157],{"className":154,"code":155,"language":156,"meta":73,"style":73},"language-yml shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","name: 'hexo deploy'\n\n## 監聽 master 分支若有 push 行為就執行\non:\n  push:\n    branches:\n    - master\njobs:\n  build:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    steps:\n    - name: Checkout\n      uses: actions\u002Fcheckout@v1\n    - name: Use Node.js 12.x\n      uses: actions\u002Fsetup-node@v1\n      with:\n        node-version: \"12.x\"\n    - name: init)init ssh\n      run: |\n          mkdir -p ~\u002F.ssh\u002F\n          echo \"${{secrets.HEXO}}\" > ~\u002F.ssh\u002Fid_rsa\n          chmod 600 ~\u002F.ssh\u002Fid_rsa\n          ssh-keyscan github.com >> ~\u002F.ssh\u002Fknown_hosts\n          git config --global user.name \"xxxx\"\n          git config --global user.email \"xxxx@gmail.com\"\n    - name: A)npm install\n      run: |\n        npm install\n    - name: B)npm install -g hexo-cli\n      run: |\n        npm install -g hexo-cli\n    - name: C) hexo d -g\n      run: |\n        hexo d -g\n","yml",[75,158,159,173,180,187,197,205,213,222,230,238,249,257,269,280,292,302,310,321,333,345,351,357,363,369,375,381,393,402,408,420,429,435,447,456],{"__ignoreMap":73},[78,160,161,165,169],{"class":80,"line":81},[78,162,164],{"class":163},"sKpQp","name",[78,166,168],{"class":167},"sMAXC",": ",[78,170,172],{"class":171},"sTRMh","'hexo deploy'\n",[78,174,176],{"class":80,"line":175},2,[78,177,179],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":178},true,"\n",[78,181,183],{"class":80,"line":182},3,[78,184,186],{"class":185},"sQrFR","## 監聽 master 分支若有 push 行為就執行\n",[78,188,190,194],{"class"